    "So... you been catching a lot o' fish?": "FishShop_16253595_29/X_Willy_event5",
    "Aha! A man after me own heart...": "FishShop_16253595_29/X_Willy_event6_male_farmer",
    "Aha! A lady after me own heart...": "FishShop_16253595_29/X_Willy_event6_female_farmer",
    "Not the fishin' type, eh? That's too bad...": "FishShop_16253595_29/X_Willy_event7",
